00:15:47.620 --> 00:15:49.620
I want one, too!

00:15:49.620 --> 00:15:52.620
Aww, well, okay, I guess.

00:15:52.620 --> 00:15:56.750
You're supposed to take
pictures of <i>all </i>of us, Yasuda!

00:15:56.750 --> 00:15:59.200
Why would I take pictures of guys?

00:15:59.200 --> 00:16:03.290
I'll grab a snapshot of you
with my eyes. There, done.

00:16:03.290 --> 00:16:07.410
Oh, come on! This is a big life moment!
Get a picture of us, please!

00:16:07.410 --> 00:16:09.040
Hori-senpai!

00:16:09.040 --> 00:16:12.700
I'm so sad I won't get to see you anymore!

00:16:12.700 --> 00:16:13.870
What's up?

00:16:13.870 --> 00:16:16.950
Y-You can still come over to see me!

00:16:16.950 --> 00:16:18.580
Really?!

00:16:18.580 --> 00:16:20.330
Not too often, though!

00:16:20.330 --> 00:16:21.700
It's her last day.

00:16:21.700 --> 00:16:24.200
Might as well let her have it, then.

00:16:27.660 --> 00:16:30.000
Our last day, huh...

00:16:34.830 --> 00:16:37.660
I'm looking for Remi, have you seen her?

00:16:37.660 --> 00:16:41.120
Oh, Ayasaki? No, I haven't.

00:16:41.120 --> 00:16:42.790
Oh.

00:16:44.830 --> 00:16:46.870
Hey, so...

00:16:46.870 --> 00:16:53.080
So, uh-- Sorry, I just...

00:16:56.580 --> 00:16:58.330
Thank you.

00:16:59.410 --> 00:17:02.870
I had so much fun this year. Really.

00:17:02.870 --> 00:17:05.080
I had the best time of my life,

00:17:05.080 --> 00:17:08.000
and part of that was
because of you, Ishikawa-kun.

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:12.250
I like you, Ishikawa-kun.
And I like Yoshikawa-san, too.

00:17:12.250 --> 00:17:14.790
I'll never forget you.

00:17:14.790 --> 00:17:18.040
Same. Neither will I.

00:17:18.040 --> 00:17:21.870
Well, good. Thanks.

00:17:21.870 --> 00:17:23.870
Yeah, same.

00:17:23.870 --> 00:17:25.500
Bye, then!

00:17:25.500 --> 00:17:28.160
Take care. See you again soon!

00:17:28.160 --> 00:17:30.080
See you later!

00:17:34.040 --> 00:17:38.250
Guess she's trying to leave
her feelings behind at school.

00:17:38.250 --> 00:17:40.160
Goodbye.

