Oh! Congratulations on graduating!

00:17:44.200 --> 00:17:45.290
Oh! Congratulations on graduating!

00:17:45.290 --> 00:17:48.500
Hey, you graduated, too! Congrats!

00:17:48.500 --> 00:17:50.580
Thank you!

00:17:50.580 --> 00:17:53.410
Oh, right! I needed to tell you something.

00:17:53.410 --> 00:17:53.500
Wh-What?!

00:17:53.500 --> 00:17:54.750 line:20%
"BA-DUMP"

00:17:53.500 --> 00:17:54.750
Wh-What?!

00:17:54.750 --> 00:17:55.250
Wh-What?!

00:17:55.250 --> 00:17:58.790
I'd like to go somewhere
with everyone after graduation.

00:17:58.790 --> 00:17:59.750
You mean as a group?

00:17:59.750 --> 00:18:04.910
Yeah. We had this conversation
with the student council the other day.

00:18:04.910 --> 00:18:06.700
It made me think, once I get my license...

00:18:06.700 --> 00:18:08.750
All of us best buds could travel!

00:18:08.750 --> 00:18:09.250
--We'll take Miyamura-kun,
Hori-san, Kono-san...

00:18:09.250 --> 00:18:11.450
--Best buds.
--We'll take Miyamura-kun,
Hori-san, Kono-san...

00:18:11.450 --> 00:18:13.950
--Just the same as always.
--We'll take Miyamura-kun,
Hori-san, Kono-san...

00:18:13.950 --> 00:18:14.620
--Sure.

00:18:14.620 --> 00:18:15.450
--Huh?
--Sure.

00:18:15.450 --> 00:18:17.330
Sounds great! Let's do it!

00:18:17.330 --> 00:18:18.200
Oh, good!

00:18:18.200 --> 00:18:19.700
Thanks for offering to drive!

00:18:19.700 --> 00:18:20.750
Huh?

00:18:20.750 --> 00:18:25.410
Nothing's going to change after
graduation, and if it does, that's fine.

00:18:25.410 --> 00:18:28.000
We'll still be friends.

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:30.290
Now there's my special boy!

00:18:30.290 --> 00:18:32.370
Kyosuke-san!

00:18:32.370 --> 00:18:33.910
Whoa, is that Miyamura-kun's dad?!

00:18:33.910 --> 00:18:34.790
He's so young!

00:18:34.790 --> 00:18:36.330
They look so similar!

00:18:36.330 --> 00:18:38.540
Similar <i>how</i>?

00:18:38.540 --> 00:18:41.370
I wanna get a picture
with my wonderful kid!

00:18:41.370 --> 00:18:43.870
Okay, let me get Hori-san--

00:18:45.540 --> 00:18:49.200
Why the hell are you here, Dad?! Huh?!

00:18:49.200 --> 00:18:51.120
I'm here to have Dad fun!

00:18:51.120 --> 00:18:54.500
Get out of here before someone
sees you in this ridiculous outfit!

00:18:55.950 --> 00:18:58.790
Miyamura! Where's <i>your </i>mom and dad?!

00:18:58.790 --> 00:19:01.870
They were here for a bit,
but had to head home for work.

00:19:01.870 --> 00:19:04.250
Man, why you gotta be so mad?

00:19:04.250 --> 00:19:07.830
Shut up and get lost!

00:19:07.830 --> 00:19:11.700
C-C'mon, now...

00:19:11.700 --> 00:19:12.750
Okay, you're good!

00:19:12.750 --> 00:19:14.580
You serious, Iura?

00:19:14.580 --> 00:19:15.660
Dead serious, dude.

00:19:15.660 --> 00:19:17.160
Big brother!

00:19:17.160 --> 00:19:19.120
Hey, Moto, you came?

00:19:19.120 --> 00:19:19.620
--Yeah.

00:19:19.620 --> 00:19:20.540
--Whoa, is this your little sister?
--Yeah.

00:19:20.540 --> 00:19:22.000
--Whoa, is this your little sister?

00:19:22.000 --> 00:19:23.160
Yup!

00:19:23.160 --> 00:19:24.950
You come to pick your big brother up?

00:19:24.950 --> 00:19:28.790
Mom said she wanted you home early.

00:19:28.790 --> 00:19:31.580
Plus I figured I could see what
my new school would be like.

00:19:31.580 --> 00:19:33.660
Wow, really?!

00:19:33.660 --> 00:19:36.700
God, that ceremony was so long!
Why'd they talk so much?

00:19:36.700 --> 00:19:40.330
Okey-dokey, let's get
our butts home, Moto!

00:19:40.330 --> 00:19:43.790
That's all, folks! Bye bye!

00:19:43.790 --> 00:19:46.080
Nice to see Iura peppy till the end.

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:48.120
All's right with the world.

00:19:51.910 --> 00:19:53.040
Big brother.

00:19:53.040 --> 00:19:55.200
Yes, little sister?

00:19:55.200 --> 00:19:57.080
Is it really you?

00:19:57.080 --> 00:19:59.000
Yep, it's me.

00:20:03.950 --> 00:20:05.620
Miyamura!

00:20:05.620 --> 00:20:09.160
We're gonna go get sushi, wanna come?!

00:20:09.160 --> 00:20:10.540
I'm in!

00:20:10.540 --> 00:20:12.500
Sweet! Let's head out, then.

00:20:12.500 --> 00:20:15.250
Kyosuke's gonna be so thrilled,
like, annoyingly so.

00:20:15.250 --> 00:20:16.700
Okay!

00:20:17.750 --> 00:20:20.000
There's no distance between us.

00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:24.200
I've never been this
close to a person before.

00:20:25.250 --> 00:20:27.580
There's no boundary between us.

00:20:27.580 --> 00:20:30.870
I used to be terrified of that.

00:20:30.870 --> 00:20:34.120
I was so scared of this, Hori-san.

00:20:34.120 --> 00:20:36.120
You know,

00:20:36.120 --> 00:20:38.000
I had no idea

00:20:38.000 --> 00:20:40.870
that I could feel

00:20:40.870 --> 00:20:42.870
so many different emotions.

00:20:44.200 --> 00:20:47.290
I don't think either of us knew

00:20:47.290 --> 00:20:51.910
how scary or nerve-wracking being
yourself around others could be.

00:20:51.910 --> 00:20:56.200
But you made me realize all of it.

00:20:56.200 --> 00:20:59.950
What can I do for you?

00:20:59.950 --> 00:21:03.620
How can I make you smile?

00:21:04.660 --> 00:21:07.870
You're so much stronger
than I think you are,

00:21:07.870 --> 00:21:13.250
and you're so much weaker
than I feel you are.

00:21:13.250 --> 00:21:15.540
You're delicate.

00:21:15.540 --> 00:21:17.700
You're fragile.

00:21:19.910 --> 00:21:25.160
That's why wherever you go,
bright, sunny days follow after.

00:21:26.160 --> 00:21:31.080
For years, the only person
I knew this well was myself.

00:21:32.750 --> 00:21:37.700
I never knew a world
like this even existed.

00:21:37.700 --> 00:21:42.040
Thank you for shattering my reality.

00:21:43.200 --> 00:21:47.620
Thank you for wanting a future with me.

00:21:50.620 --> 00:21:53.830
What can I do for <i>you</i>?

00:21:53.830 --> 00:21:56.830
How can I repay you for what you've done?

00:21:58.830 --> 00:22:02.040
C'mon, Miyamura!

00:22:07.540 --> 00:22:09.950
Oh.

00:22:09.950 --> 00:22:13.620
The spring sky is bluer
than I've ever seen.

00:22:13.620 --> 00:22:19.870
If only I could gift you
this wonderful sky.

00:22:19.870 --> 00:22:24.660
No, I know what you'd like better.

00:22:24.660 --> 00:22:29.790
A cake with lots of whipped cream on top.